            "body": "Run into that problem. My current solution is a mix of langmaps and normal maps since one seems needed for repeated mappings like ]] and the other for plugins that use noremaps. I mostly use it to bring ä and ü to square brackets because a lot of things use them and since I use enter for :  anyway which makes the number of remaps KIND of bearable.\n\nAn actual viable way to make this work on a bigger scale would be awesome, though.\n",
